text: Alice Stoffel (30 October 1905 - 22 August 1983) was a French swimmer. She competed at the 1924 Summer Olympics and the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1905 births Category:1983 deaths Category:French female swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of France Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Colmar
